= Iwik Changelog

== Version 0.10.0

* Use external ri18n project for internationalization (ri18n-0.0.1)
* Support interpolation in translation messages
* First i18n work
* A lot of small url fixes (routing)

== initial import:

* Refactored chunks and wiki_content.rb 
* Fixed broken links in edit_web
* Fixed the "All Pages" link (list.rhtml)
* actionpack: url_for hotfix
* hard_break option for Redcloth on by default
	
== initial Instiki working copy:

* revision 173
* railties + actionpack + activesupport : revision 901 
	
	
